text: Óscar Jaenada Gajo (born 4 May 1975) is a Spanish actor. He is known for his roles as the Spainard pirate in Pirates of the Caribbean: On Stranger Tides and as Cantinflas in the 2014 movie about his life. ==References== Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:Spanish movie actors Category:Spanish television actors Category:Spanish voice actors Category:Spanish stage actors
